---

<footer class="bg-[#0A0A0A] border-t border-white/10 pt-16 pb-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
    <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">KILO <span class="text-[#F5C518]">TAXI SERVICE</span></h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm max-w-sm leading-relaxed">မြန်မာ့ပထမဆုံး Kilo-based စနစ်ဖြင့် စိတ်ချယုံကြည်စွာ သွားလာနိုင်မည့် Premium တက္ကစီဝန်ဆောင်မှု။</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">လင့်ခ်များ</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <li><a href="#home" class="hover:text-[#F5C518] transition-colors">ပင်မစာမျက်နှာ</a></li>
        <li><a href="#history" class="hover:text-[#F5C518] transition-colors">သမိုင်းမှတ်တမ်း</a></li>
        <li><a href="#application" class="hover:text-[#F5C518] transition-colors">App ရယူရန်</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-4">ဆက်သွယ်ရန်</h3>
      <div class="flex gap-4">
        {socialLinks.map(link => (
          <a 
            href={link.url} 
            target="_blank" 
            title={link.name}
            class={`w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-white/5 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-400 ${link.color} hover:text-white hover:scale-110 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 ease-out`}
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d={link.icon} />
            </svg>
          </a>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/5 text-center text-gray-600 text-xs">
    © 2026 Kilo Taxi Service. All rights reserved.
  </div>
</footer>